	"system": {
		"description": "<p>You can imprint your thoughts, memories, or visions into fire. As an action, you touch a flame and record a message, sensation, or memory no longer than 1 minute. Anyone who touches or gazes into the flame experiences the memory as a vivid illusion. You can have a number of Edicts of the Archivist active at the same time equal to your Constitution modifier.</p>",
